phrases: Who could it be this early in the morning?
It is a tad too early for newspaper salesmen to be visiting.
My apologies for disturbing you this early.
I just moved in next door the other day.
I was quite rude when we first met last night
and undoubtedly inconvenienced you, so I would like to apologize and show my gratitude.
Here is a little something as my greeting and thanks.
but I have heard that noodles are among the best gifts to give out when you move in somewhere.
Maou and I go way back.
I have heard about you two.
I have not met the landlord here,
but she said in her letter that I should rely on you if I ever need help.
That letter also contained a photograph...
That letter also contained a photograph...
Oh, that is definitely from the landlord.
Anyway, I feel much reassured to know I have neighbors I can rely on.
I would be much obliged if you deigned to guide me in the ways of the apartment.
The ways of the apartment, she says.
Yeah, a recent addition to the residents here.
He is also a total bum.
I am not doing this because I want to!
Then why are you doing this again?
It all starts right here, right now
Let us picture what we can do
Let us picture what we can do
Let us picture what we can do
But we can overcome them all
But we can overcome them all
But we can overcome them all
Our dreams are born from nothing
And take us to that shining sky
And take us to that shining sky
And take us to that shining sky
And take us to that shining sky
I want to spread my wings
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Now here I go, with the greatest smile on my face
Let us set out to an unknown world
Let us set out to an unknown world
Let us set out to an unknown world
Let us set out to an unknown world
We will be the ones to choose and decide the future
Let us chase after our dreams
There will be times when we cry
I have a really important wish
I am sure you will be able to meet your future self
I am sure you will be able to meet your future self
I am sure you will be able to meet your future self
I had it manufactured in a form that you could store in Japan without having it stick out like a sore thumb.
It is not B. It is Beta!
So what, drinking this will replenish my sacred powers?
But be careful with the dosage.
Is there a recommended amount or something?
Consider the limit to be two bottles per day.
Take one in the morning and one in the afternoon,
but do not drink two in the afternoon just because you forgot to take the morning dose or something.
I kind of get it now.
Make sure you know the directions, the dosage, and how to use it properly!
Just where is she right now?
Well, it cannot hurt to try it out.
Why is it so hot each and every day?
And those guys do not seem to be up to anything, either.
I get the feeling I am just wasting my blood, sweat, and tears here...
It is all about perspective, girl!
So what if the Overlord faction's just working like normal folk every day in order to put food on the table?
you could say I am just stalking some veterans who are peacefully living out their days.
Do you know not how to even dry garments?
You really have no idea how to do any chores, do you, Hanzou?
It will lose its shape if you put it out to dry all wrinkled up.
That will just ruin the sides.
It really feels like there is another Ashiya now.
What on earth is going on?
This is a bit risky, but I do not have a choice here, do I?
You have to be more responsible now, Hanzou.
You chop up the spring onions and then churn it.
Then you dilute the paste with cold water.
With just this, your meal's ready as long as you boil the udon noodles.
And if you soak them in cold water once they are done boiling, voila!
Add some raw egg, and they will be perfect.
I got to boil noodles in this heat?
You will be eating this for every meal, every day.
Would it not be prudent to spice things up a bit?
The rest of us are white noise to him.
You know how to use a grater at least, do not you?
Are we out of ginger, Ashiya?
Come to think of it, I think we used it all up yesterday.
Will spring onions do for today?
Urushihara, the fridge is not an air conditioner!
What the heck are these people doing?
I will go get some ginger from my apartment.
Do you have to fall down every flight of stairs you see?!
You are a hero, so you should really stop doing that.
The hell are you two doing?
It was my fault for suddenly opening the door.
I just lost my footing because I was careless.
And you call yourself a hero?
I grabbed everything I could find lying out there.
Keep drinking stuff like that you will get heatstroke like Ashiya over there.
I should have picked something more nutritious.
It is not your fault, Kamazuki.
I have not introduced myself yet.
I moved in next door last week.
I hail from an old-fashioned family in a faraway land,
so I am still not accustomed to this place.
I would be much obliged if you could teach me the ways of the city.
I guess we are about the same size...
Man, there is so much to do and learn.
It is wearing me out here.
But you have been working for ages now.
You may have been idling your days away,
but I have grown immensely as a human!
Hold it right there, did you really just call yourself human?
From Sunday, the day after tomorrow,
I am a shift supervisor at the Hatagaya Station MgRonald's!
I am going to be an assistant manager!
You do not believe me, do you?
A shift supervisor holds great responsibility, and the pay reflects that!
What I find most unbelievable is that you are seriously bragging to me about that.
In time, I will reach heights that you cannot even imagine!
How dare you speak like that to the master of this house?
You will not get away with it!
Emi, are you perhaps in a close relationship with Sadao?
You have got to be kidding me!
You two seem very unreserved with each other.
Do not poke your nose where it does not belong!
but we do not share any trust, friendship, or the least bit of positive feelings toward each other.
In fact, if he just dropped dead, it would pretty much make my day,
I get the feeling I have gone through this before...
I do not believe for one second that it is true,
but are you going after Maou too?!
Are you out of your mind?
I did not think it was really the case...
I probably should not tell her that this has happened once before.
Your intuition's as good as ever.
At first, I thought she was an assassin from another world,
but it would be weird for an assassin to not do anything for a whole week after moving in,
and she is too polite to me to be a demon.
You might think this is all a bit too complicated, but hear me out.
You should not get too close to him.
It will only because you sorrow.
He is not a man that any normal person can deal with.
You should stay away from him if you can.
I-I might not look it, but I have overcome loads of battles in the past.
If you insist this much, however, I will be careful.
I am sure there is something behind all this that only you can understand.
That said, it is too late for me to leave this place.
I am fully aware this is impudent of me, but please give me your assistance.
I will do what I can.
I sure hope you did not do anything weird while I was not around.
I am not that much of a daredevil.
Here is my address, phone number, and my e-mail address.
Feel free to ask for help any time these guys do something to you.
Just what the hell do you think we are?
Blood-thirsty monsters that are worse than cockroaches, that is what.
I do not think you will,
but if you dare try something on Suzuno,
I will chop off your head and leave it hanging to dry at that window over there.
What are you supposed to be, an evil magistrate?
Well, it is about time I leave.
You do not have to worry.
They might not look it, but they are law-abiding citizens.
Was that a scream I just heard?
No, she managed to grab on to something halfway down.
You do not have to see me off.
Man, dealing with Emi drains all my energy.
Did she do anything rude to you?
I am off to work, then.
Um... take this, if it pleases you.
Is the Holy Vitamin Beta working?
Well, I have been drinking it,
but I have not had a chance to see its effects.
It is been a while since I have needed to fight.
How is it going with the Overlord?
We start arguing the moment we see each other,
and we are both busy with work, so we do not have time to get in each other's business.
You sound like the wife who complains about how she cannot spend time with her husband because of work.
I am a Hero of Ente Isle, and he is the Overlord!
He will be my enemy until the end of time!
Just thinking about it sends chills down my spine!
I kept watch on him this morning, and I am still doing so!
You do not know what I have been through!
do not do anything that would make me have to turn on you.
I swear on the names of my parents that I will never do anything wrong.
how have things been over there recently?
None of the countries are showing any signs of movement on the surface.
I do hear all kinds of rumors,
but who knows if they are true?
It seems the Church is trying to get to the bottom of Olba's disappearance.
There might even be people looking for you.
Some of them could get hasty and because problems in Japan.
A Hero's job is never done, huh?
Anyway, I do not want to rack up a massive bill from talking too long,
so I will hang up now.
tomorrow will see the opening of what will likely be a formidable opponent,
I will be gone in the afternoon,
so it is up to you to carry our business on your shoulders, Maou.
Of course, you can still contact me in case of an emergency,
but unless it is critical, you may make decisions on my behalf.
This will help you grow, too.
We do not have many people on shift tonight, so stay alert.
You may consider that your job as shift supervisor has already begun.
Anyway, take a break while you can.
Or would you rather get a staff meal here?
Figured I would grab a bite.
That is kind of a tasteful lunch box.
Nah, someone lent it to me.
Someone moved in next door recently, actually.
Do not just yell out of the blue!
You borrowed a lunch box from her?
What is the meaning of this?!
D-Does that mean the girl next door gave you her...
Yeah, but please... stop shaking me!
Do not tell me it is handmade!
Could you let m-m-m-me have a look?!
To take a look at what is underneath?
I have a baaad feeling about this.
I ended up coming this far,
but if I can turn back here,
I keep buying the same one every time.
Also, hurry up and call the cops!
I do not know if you are human or a demon,
but you have got some nerve to attack me in such a conspicuous location.
What do you think you are doing?
It would be one thing if it was just me,
but if you are going to because problems for the other people here,
I am not going to show you any mercy!
Sorry I pushed you like that.
I just got a little scuff on my forehead.
The alarm should have alerted the security firm and the police.
I am sorry, but our employee manual says to not let the customers leave when stuff like this happens.
The police are on their way, so could you please wait a while?
The Better Half I summoned this time
contained a lot more power than it did during the battle against Lucifer two months ago.
I might even be able to call the Robe of the Vanquisher.
That purple beam completely has me stumped, though.
I have never met an enemy who could nullify the sacred sword and my powers.
Um, I believe this is yours.
You would never guess I like this kind of stuff.
A-A-A handmade lunch with a heart mark on it!
A girl gave him a two-layered box!
Where in this silent sky does the sun rise?
A promise I made while pretending to not see it
Being a liar and a coward
If I was at fault for everything
Then our promise might only have been a fleeting dream
I managed to hide it in the shadow of the moonlight
My tears will not flow anymore
If I was able to let everything go
I might be able to cry again
But this world is full of things I want to protect
